net.engio.daoism.dao

Interface ITypedDao<KEY extends Serializable,E extends Persistent<KEY>>

  • Type Parameters:
    KEY - The type of primary key used for the Persistent
    E - The type of domain object the instance of ITypedDao works on
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TypedDao

    public interface ITypedDao<KEY extends Serializable,E extends Persistent<KEY>>
    A typed version of the IPersistenceProvider interface. It provides type-safe method for domain object persistence.
    Author:
    Benjamin Diedrichsen
